---
import DocLayout from '../../layouts/DocLayout.astro';
---

<DocLayout title="API 参考" description="完整的 API 参考文档。">
  <div class="prose">
    <h1>API 参考</h1>
    <p>所有端点和方法的详细 API 文档。</p>

    <h2>端点</h2>

    <h3>GET /api/v1/resources</h3>
    <p>获取资源列表。</p>
    <p><strong>查询参数：</strong></p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>参数</th><th>类型</th><th>描述</th><th>必填</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>page</td><td>number</td><td>页码</td><td>否</td></tr>
        <tr><td>limit</td><td>number</td><td>每页条数</td><td>否</td></tr>
        <tr><td>sort</td><td>string</td><td>排序字段</td><td>否</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p><strong>响应示例：</strong></p>
    <pre><code>&lcub;
  &quot;data&quot;: [
    &lcub;
      &quot;id&quot;: &quot;res_001&quot;,
      &quot;name&quot;: &quot;示例资源&quot;,
      &quot;created_at&quot;: &quot;2026-07-07T00:00:00Z&quot;
    &rcub;
  ],
  &quot;meta&quot;: &lcub;
    &quot;page&quot;: 1,
    &quot;limit&quot;: 20,
    &quot;total&quot;: 1
  &rcub;
&rcub;</code></pre>

    <h3>POST /api/v1/resources</h3>
    <p>创建新资源。</p>
    <p><strong>请求体：</strong></p>
    <pre><code>&lcub;
  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;新资源&quot;,
  &quot;description&quot;: &quot;资源描述&quot;
&rcub;</code></pre>
    <p><strong>响应：</strong> <code>201 Created</code></p>

    <h2>错误响应</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>状态码</th><th>含义</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>400</td><td>请求错误</td></tr>
        <tr><td>401</td><td>未授权</td></tr>
        <tr><td>404</td><td>未找到</td></tr>
        <tr><td>500</td><td>服务器内部错误</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>认证</h2>
    <p>所有 API 请求需要在 <code>Authorization</code> 头中携带 API Key：</p>
    <pre><code>curl -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY&quot; \
  https://api.example.com/v1/resources</code></pre>
  </div>
</DocLayout>
